Name: Epic Ragnr Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Greater Ragnr Rune, Level 4 Spell Slot
Description: This rune symbolizes destruction and chaos, allowing those who channel it to tap into the power of destruction.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACECorruptionSPACEAs an action, you can lash out at a creature with destructive energy. Make a melee spell attack against a creature within your reach. On a hit, the target takes DAMAGE3-6DAMAGEd8 necrotic damage and has disadvantage on the next ability check or saving throw it makes before the end of your next turn.SPACESPACEField of EntropySPACEAs a bonus action, you can conjure forth an aura of corroding energy in a DISTANCE15-20DISTANCE foot radius centered on you for TIME3-5TIME rounds or until you end the effect. All creatures that start their turn within or enter the aura must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or have their armor class reduced by DAMAGE2-3DAMAGE for the duration. This has no effect on magical or natural armor.SPACESPACERunic SmiteSPACEAs an action, you call down the power of chaos on a creature of your choice within DISTANCE30-45DISTANCE feet of you that you can see. The target must make a Dexterity saving throw, taking DAMAGE3-5DAMAGEd10 necrotic damage and being knocked prone on a failed save, or half as much damage and not being knocked prone on a successful one. While prone as a result of this effect, the target must use all of its movement speed to stand up and cannot take the Dash action on the same turn.SPACESPACEAnnihilationSPACEAs an action, you unleash a wave of destructive force mingled with crippling despair. All creatures of your choice within a DISTANCE10-15DISTANCE foot radius sphere centered on you must make a Constitution saving throw, taking DAMAGE4-6DAMAGEd10 necrotic damage and it suffers 1 level of exhaustion on a failed save or half as much damage and no levels of exhaustion on a successful one. A creature may suffer a maximum of DAMAGE2-3DAMAGE levels of exhaustion as a result of this effect. A creature that succeeds on its saving throw is immune to this effect for the next 24 hours.SPACESPACEYou may use this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest.
